title: Lower Unit for 10/1, Updated Kitchen, Garage, All Utilities Included!
posting_body: ['Lower Duplex Available October 1, Updated Kitchen & Flooring, All Utilities Included,', 'One Garage Stall', 'Property Address', '477 Macalester St - Lower Unit | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do a showing once an application is approved.', ' Each adult would apply at <URL> and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Lower duplex available October 1 in Mac Groveland just blocks from Macalester College.', ' Open floor plan throughout the whole apartment.', ' The living room has open arches leading to the bedroom.', ' Bedroom has an attached bathroom with tiled shower.', ' Kitchen has all updated cabinets, countertops and appliances.', ' Updated flooring throughout!', " There's a closet in the bedroom and a cedar lined closet in the living room.", ' ', "There's shared laundry in the duplex, and this apartment includes one garage stall.", ' Private entrance on the side.', 'All utilities are included!', 'Cats are okay with a $35/month pet fee per.', ' Sorry no dogs.', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 610', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,081.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,081.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
